title: David Kalivoda
text: David Kalivoda (born 25 August 1982, in <a href="Lede%C4%8D%20nad%20S%C3%A1zavou">Ledeč nad Sázavou</a>) is a <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech</a> <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> player who currently plays for <a href="1.%20FK%20P%C5%99%C3%ADbram">1. FK Příbram</a>. He is a midfielder.
